ucing%20its%20own%20sleeping%20bags%20and%20parkas%20in%201973.%20In%201976%2C%20it%20became%20the%20first%20outdoor%20brand%20to%20use%20GORE-TEX%2C%20a%20waterproof%20yet%20breathable%20fabric%2C%20in%20its%20gear.%20Fifty%20years%20later%2C%20the%20brand%20is%20still%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20performance%20and%20still%20uses%20GORE-TEX%20in%20its%20jackets%20simply%20because%20it's%20just%20that%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Marmot%20GORE-TEX%20Mammoth%20Parka%20is%20the%20brand's%20most%20popular%20parka%20design.%20Fit%20for%20expeditions%20and%20street%20use%20alike%2C%20it%20features%20a%20two-layer%20waterproof%20GORE-TEX%20fabric%2C%20and%20tape-sealed%20seams%20to%20prevent%20leaks.%20While%20many%20other%20parkas%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20waterproofing%20technology%2C%20GORE-TEX%20is%20by%20far%20my%20favorite%20technology%20because%20it%20keeps%20water%20from%20getting%20in%2C%20but%20allows%20built-up%20moisture%20from%20your%20body%20to%20escape%20the%20garment.%20I've%20worn%20boots%2C%20hats%2C%20hoodies%2C%20and%20many%20jackets%20featuring%20the%20technology%20and%20they've%20all%20impressed%20me%20with%20how%20well%20they%20hold%20up%20to%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20700-fill%20power%20rating%2C%20the%20Marmot%20Mammoth%20is%20incredibly%20warm%20and%20has%20plenty%20of%20features%20that%20make%20it%20usable%20for%20anything%20the%20winter%20has%20to%20offer.%20The%20powder%20skirt%20is%20a%20great%20feature%20for%20snow%20sports%20from%20snow%20tubing%20to%20more%20extreme%20sports%20like%20snowboarding.%20You'll%20also%20find%20fleece-lined%20hand%20warmer%20pockets%20on%20the%20outside%20and%20convenient%20media%20pockets%20on%20the%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitting%20of%20the%20Mammoth%20name%2C%20this%20parka%20is%20slightly%20oversized%2C%20so%20I%20recommend%20going%20true%20to%20size.%20However%2C%20adjustable%20drawcords%20at%20the%20waist%20and%20Velcro%20cuffs%20allow%20you%20to%20adjust%20the%20fit%20to%20your%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20sustainable%3A%20Fj%C3%A4llr%C3%A4ven%20Expedition%20Down%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222055%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%20wearing%20a%20black%20Fjallraven%20Expedition%20Down%20Jacket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65831c06cefc010bea259eaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221541%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOriginally%20released%20in%201974%2C%20the%20Expedition%20Down%20Jacket%20is%20one%20of%20Fjallraven's%20most%20iconic%20designs.%20It%20was%20initially%20created%20for%20cold-weather%20explorers%20who%20needed%20serious%20protection%20from%20sub-freezing%20temperatures%2C%20and%20its%20current%20version%20serves%20the%20same%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20many%20winter%20coats%20and%20parkas%20I've%20tested%2C%20the%20Expedition%20Down%20Jacket%20is%20excellent%20if%20staying%20warm%20is%20your%20primary%20objective.%20The%20jacket%20has%20a%20700-fill%20power%2C%20a%20below-the-hip%20length%20to%20block%20out%20the%20cold%2C%20an%20adjustable%20alpine%20hood%2C%20an%20adjustable%20hem%2C%20two-way%20zippers%2C%20a%20durable%20water-resistant%20outer%20lining%2C%20and%20adjustable%20sleeves.%20And%20the%20most%20surprising%20feature%20of%20all%20is%20that%20it's%20packable%20%E2%80%94%20something%20unheard%20of%20for%20jackets%20this%20big.%20In%20terms%20of%20function%2C%20I%20can't%20think%20of%20a%20single%20feature%20I%20wish%20it%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Expedition%20Down%20Jacket%20is%20as%20no-nonsense%20as%20winter%20coats%20come%2C%20its%20oversized%20fit%20makes%20it%20less%20practical%20for%20daily%20use.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20found%20it%20uncomfortable%20and%20difficult%20to%20drive%20my%20car%20while%20wearing%20it.%20If%20you%20love%20the%20style%2C%20but%20want%20a%20jacket%20that's%20a%20bit%20more%20practical%20(and%20affordable)%2C%20I%20also%20recommend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D24ac488fd3785fa85a1908492d94aa028e135151dc6cab5bcb8c6f86dc916cfb%26postID%3D69726e64a1e4d776a36947d4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-parkas-men%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.fjallraven.com%252Fus%252Fen-us%252Fmen%252Fjackets%252Fwinter-jackets%252Fexpedition-down-lite-jacket-m%253Fv%253DF84605%25253a%25253a7323450930455%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExpedition%20Down%20Lite%20Jacket%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20stylish%3A%20The%20North%20Face%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20standing%20on%20the%20sidewalk%20wearing%20the%20The%20North%20Face%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65832c97cefc010bea25abf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20The%20North%20Face%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20outdoor%20performance%2C%20some%20of%20its%20most%20technical%20cold-weather%20designs%20have%20been%20adopted%20in%20fashion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20the%20original%20Himalayan%20Down%20Parka%2C%20the%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20high-alpine%20gear%20and%20streetwear%20fashion.%20As%20a%20toned-down%20version%20of%20the%20original%2C%20the%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%20features%20the%20iconic%20retro%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20The%20North%20Face%20parkas%20with%20large%20down-filled%20baffles%20and%20bold%20color-blocking%2C%20while%20being%20more%20comfortable%20for%20daily%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jacket%20features%20550-fill%20power%20down%2C%20durable%20water-resistant%20coating%2C%20adjustable%20cords%20on%20the%20hem%20and%20hood%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20interior%20and%20exterior%20storage%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%20is%20a%20great%20choice%20of%20men's%20winter%20coats%20for%20people%20who%20love%20the%20look%20of%20burly%20parkas%20like%20the%20original%20Himalayan%20Down%20Parka%2C%20but%20have%20no%20intentions%20of%20scaling%20any%20mountains.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20it's%20more%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20I%20tested%20for%20the%20best%20parkas%20for%20men%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20guide%2C%20I%20tested%20each%20parka%20in%20the%20real%20world%20over%20several%20winter%20seasons.%20Each%20parka%20was%20worn%20during%20the%20coldest%20months%20of%20the%20year.%20I%20considered%20the%20overall%20warmth%2C%20water%20resistance%2C%20comfort%2C%20bulkiness%2C%20style%2C%20and%20important%20design%20features%20like%20adjustable%20cuffs%2C%20hand%20warmer%20pockets%2C%20and%20removable%20hoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20considered%20testing%20a%20variety%20of%20styles%20to%20meet%20different%20people's%20needs%20and%20budgets.%20Some%20parkas%20are%20designed%20for%20more%20technical%20use%2C%20but%20my%20testing%20was%20based%20on%20everyday%20wear%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20average%20person%20would%20wear%20them%20%E2%80%94%20outside%20a%20controlled%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20brands%20sustainably%20use%20down%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sustainability%20and%20ethics%20surrounding%20down%20and%20fur%20are%20inherently%20points%20of%20contention.%20The%20animal%20welfare%20of%20waterfowl%20is%20slightly%20more%20clear-cut%20and%20traceable%3A%20Many%20of%20the%20brands%20in%20our%20guide%2C%20including%20Fjallraven%20and%20Triple%20F.A.T.%20Goose%2C%20put%20their%20down%20through%20rigorous%20testing%20to%20identify%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20down%20was%20plucked%20from%20live%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETriple%20F.A.T.%20Goose%20puts%20its%20down%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idfl.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Down%20and%20Feather%20Testing%20Laboratory%20(IDFL)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20meet%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fresponsibledown.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2FTE-Responsible-Down-Standard-2.0-opt.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResponsible%20Down%20Standard%20(RDS)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%20there's%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nsf.org%2Fnewsroom_pdf%2Fsu_traceble_down_infopaper.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Traceable%20Down%20Standard%20(Global%20TDS)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20certified%20by%20the%20NSF%20and%20slightly%20more%20rigorous%20in%20requiring%20parent%20farm%20certification.%20That%20means%20that%20whatever%20farm%20an%20egg%20or%20a%20hatchling%20came%20from%20must%20be%20certified%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20the%20RDS%20and%20Global%20TDS%20are%20almost%20identical%2C%20and%20both%20essentially%20uphold%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aspca.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Faspca_asv_five_freedoms_final1.ashx_.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFive%20Freedoms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20ducks%20and%20geese%20whose%20feathers%20and%20down%20are%20collected%20are%20not%20force-fed%2C%20live-plucked%2C%20malnourished%2C%20or%20transported%20from%20farm%20to%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20fill%20power%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFill%20power%20is%20a%20number%20that%20measures%20the%20amount%20of%20space%20one%20ounce%20of%20down%20will%20fill%20in%20cubic%20inches.%20Higher%20fill%20power%20is%20an%20indication%20of%20higher%20quality%20down%20being%20used%20and%20a%20warmer%20garment%20for%20the%20wearer.%20The%20higher%20the%20fill%20power%2C%20the%20better%20the%20down%20can%20trap%20your%20body%20heat%20and%20keep%20you%20warm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20brands%20still%20use%20real%20fur%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20do%2C%20yes.%20Fur%20can%20come%20from%20animals%20that%20have%20been%20farmed%20(as%20is%20often%20the%20case%20with%20foxes%20and%20minks)%2C%20or%20it%20can%20come%20from%20wild%20animals.%20Coyote%20fur%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20what%20you'll%20see%20adorning%20parkas%2C%20is%20generally%20trapped%20or%20hunted.%20A%20lot%20of%20brands%20source%20coyote%20fur%20from%20places%20where%20they're%20deemed%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20species%2C%20either%20by%20way%20of%20overpopulation%2C%20mange%2C%20or%20invasiveness.%20Blue%20fox%20is%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20fox%20fur%20used%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20is%20often%20sourced%20from%20farms%20certified%20by%20Nordic%20fur%20trading%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sagafurs.com%2Fsustainability%2Fcertification%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaga%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20brands%20disclose%20their%20own%20use%20of%20fur%2C%20a%20general%20practice%20is%20to%20list%20their%20compliance%20and%20cooperation%20with%20game%20trapping%20laws%20and%20standards%20set%20forth%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffur.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2FAIHTS-Copy-of-Agreement.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAgreement%20on%20International%20Humane%20Trapping%20Standards%20(AIHTS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canada%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fishwildlife.org%2Fafwa-inspires%2Ffurbearer-management%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBest%20Management%20Practices%20(BMP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20standards%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFur%20does%20indeed%20have%20moisture-wicking%20properties%20and%20warmth%20that%20no%20synthetic%20material%20can%20match.%20But%20we%20see%20it%20being%20phased%20out%20by%20more%20and%20more%20brands%2C%20as%20public%20opinion%20has%20generally%20shifted%20towards%20%26quot%3Bcruelty%20free%26quot%3B%2