.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2F6-year-old-walks-two-miles-for-help-after-father-dies-saving-him-in-upstate-new-york-ice-tragedy%2Famp_articleshow%2F127195488.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2F6-year-old-walks-two-miles-for-help-after-father-dies-saving-him-in-upstate-new-york-ice-tragedy%2Famp_articleshow%2F127195488.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20Housemaid'%3A%20How%20Sydney%20Sweeney's%20scrappy%20thriller%20became%20the%20%24240%20million%20box-office%20hit%20no%20one%20saw%20coming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20Seyfried%20and%20Sydney%20Sweeney%20smiling%20in%20The%20Housemaid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696f71cee1ba468a96aa5382%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Amanda%20Seyfried%20and%20Sydney%20Sweeney%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ELionsgate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20surprise%20hit%20at%20the%20global%20box%20office%2C%20earning%20over%20%24200%20million%20on%20a%20%2435%20million%20budget.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProducer%20Todd%20Lieberman%20explained%20how%20the%20movie%20became%20an%20unlikely%20success%20story.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20sequel%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid's%20Secret%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20already%20in%20the%20works.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChristmastime%20is%20typically%20filled%20with%20presents%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20and%202025%20had%20a%20sack%20full%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-cameron-movies-billions-box-office-greatest-directors-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJames%20Cameron%3C%2Fa%3E's%20big-budget%20juggernaut%20%26quot%3BAvatar%3A%20Fire%20%26amp%3B%20Ash%26quot%3B%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20another%20billion-dollar%20earner%2C%20while%20the%20A24%20drama%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme%26quot%3B%20found%20its%20audience%20thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarty-supreme-marketing-campaign-why-it-worked-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETimoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet's%20hip%20marketing%20gimmicks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20cultural%20conversation%20was%20occupied%20by%20blockbuster%20blue%20people%20and%20a%20ping-pong%20phenom%2C%20one%20R-rated%20thriller%20was%20slowly%20gaining%20buzz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20lacked%20in%20eye-popping%20visuals%20and%20critical%20cachet%20it%20made%20up%20for%20in%20star%20power%20and%20a%20racy%20storyline.%20Made%20for%20just%20%2435%20million%20%E2%80%94%20a%20budget%20nowhere%20near%20that%20of%20%26quot%3BAvatar%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20is%20adapted%20from%20the%20bestselling%20novel%20of%20the%20same%20name%20and%20directed%20by%20Paul%20Feig%20(%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbridesmaids-paul-feig-film-secrets-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBridesmaids%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BA%20Simple%20Favor%26quot%3B).%20It%20stars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsydney-sweeney-best-worst-movie-tv-roles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESydney%20Sweeney%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20titular%20young%20housemaid%20with%20a%20troubled%20past%2C%20who's%20hired%20by%20Nina%20(Amanda%20Seyfried)%2C%20an%20eccentric%20housewife%20who%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20(Brandon%20Sklenar)%2C%20have%20some%20dark%20secrets%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20indication%20the%20movie%20was%20becoming%20an%20unlikely%20success%20story%20was%20its%20surprising%20international%20performance%2C%20earning%20over%20%24100%20million%20overseas%20by%20the%20first%20weekend%20in%20January.%20The%20movie%20hit%20its%20stride%20this%20past%20weekend%2C%20crossing%20the%20%24100%20million%20milestone%20domestically%2C%20giving%20the%20Lionsgate%20thriller%20a%20remarkable%20worldwide%20total%20of%20over%20%24240%20million.%20It's%20now%20the%20biggest%20hit%20of%20Sweeney's%20career%20and%20a%20bona%20fide%20sleeper%20hit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20producer%20Todd%20Lieberman%2C%20the%20movie's%20success%20was%20hardly%20a%20surprise.%20From%20producing%20past%20overperformers%20like%20the%202010%20Oscar-winning%20boxing%20drama%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fighter%26quot%3B%20to%202017's%20hit%20coming-of-age%20tale%20%26quot%3BWonder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20an%20eye%20for%20modest-budget%20material%20that%20will%20draw%20in%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20sleeper%20hit%20is%20fun%20because%20you%20know%20it's%20not%20a%20sleeper%2C%20but%20everyone%20else%20thinks%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%2C%20Lieberman%20explains%20how%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20became%20the%20latest%20Hollywood%20success%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f021fa49-7268-4c5c-b095-74e2a79ee779%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20book%20before%20it%20blows%20up%20and%20optioning%20it%20first%20was%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amanda%20Seyfied%20burning%20a%20paper%20in%20The%20Housemaid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696f7245e1ba468a96aa538a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmanda%20Seyfried%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EDaniel%20McFadden%2FLionsgate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%2020%20years%20alongside%20David%20Hoberman%20as%20the%20owners%20of%20Mandeville%20Films%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20highlights%20include%20the%202009%20Ryan%20Reynolds%20and%20Sandra%20Bullock%20rom-com%20%26quot%3BThe%20Proposal%26quot%3B%20and%20Disney's%202017%20live-action%20%26quot%3BBeauty%20and%20the%20Beast%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Lieberman%20went%20out%20on%20his%20own%2C%20launching%20the%20production%20company%20Hidden%20Pictures%20in%202022.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20projects%20he%20went%20courting%20was%20adapting%20Frieda%20McFadden's%20novel%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20read%20the%20book%2C%20and%20I%20just%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20said%2C%20giving%20credit%20to%20his%20VP%20of%20development%2C%20Carly%20Elter%2C%20for%20passing%20him%20the%20novel.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20see%20the%20twist.%20I%20felt%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20we're%20looking%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20learning%20a%20major%20studio%20was%20also%20looking%20to%20acquire%20the%20book%20rights%2C%20Lieberman%20brought%20in%20Lionsgate%2C%20the%20company's%20financial%20partner%2C%20for%20some%20extra%20muscle.%20Eventually%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20nab%20not%20just%20the%20rights%20to%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20other%20two%20books%20in%20McFadden's%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid's%20Secret%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%20Is%20Watching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20time%20that%20Hidden%20Pictures%20hired%20Rebecca%20Sonnenshine%20(%26quot%3BThe%20Boys%26quot%3B)%20to%20write%20the%20script%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20began%20having%20a%20surge%20in%20book%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20taking%20a%20trajectory%20like%20what%20we%20had%20experienced%20with%20'Wonder%2C'%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20movie%20he%20produced%20starring%20Jacob%20Tremblay%20as%20a%20boy%20with%20a%20facial%20disfigurement%20who%20navigates%20public%20school%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20R.J.%20Palacio%20book%20of%20the%20same%20name%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20bestseller%20before%20the%20film's%20release%2C%20ultimately%20boosting%20the%20adaptation's%20popularity%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20over%20%24300%20million%20at%20the%20global%20box%20office%20on%20a%20%2422%20million%20budget.%20It's%20since%20been%20translated%20into%2029%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20could%20see%20the%20book%20was%20selling%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20copies%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20said%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid.%26quot%3B%20It%2C%20too%2C%20would%20go%20on%20to%20become%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20bestseller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20movie%20still%20wasn't%20greenlit%20at%20the%20studio.%20So%20Lieberman%20and%20his%20team%20put%20together%20what%20he%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BBrag%20Pack%26quot%3B%20for%20Lionsgate%20filled%20with%20data%20and%20accolades%20to%20up%20the%20project's%20chances%2C%20showcasing%20how%20many%20books%20had%20been%20sold%2C%20the%20awards%20the%20books%20were%20up%20for%2C%20and%20the%20groundswell%20of%20fandom%20on%20social%20media%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20was%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20primed%20at%20that%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cded0a8-c2ed-422b-88bb-6599f9238d16%5C%22%3ETiming%20was%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20accommodating%20Sydney%20Sweeney's%20schedule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sydney%20Sweeney%20sitting%20next%20to%20a%20doll%20house%20in%20The%20Housemaid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696f758ea645d11881879c06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESydney%20Sweeney%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EDaniel%20McFadden%2FLionsgate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20late%20fall%202024%2C%20Lionsgate%20interest%20in%20the%20project%20had%20increased%2C%20as%20Hidden%20Pictures%20had%20signed%20a%20director%20and%20gotten%20Sweeney%20involved%20to%20play%20Millie.%20But%20there%20were%20also%20some%20complexities%20to%20navigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSydney%20had%20a%20very%20limited%20window%20to%20shoot%20this%20movie%20because%20she%20had%20'Euphoria'%20that%20was%20toggling%20between%20certain%20dates%2C%20so%20she%20was%20locked%20in%20for%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20time.%20We%20had%20literally%2032%20days%20to%20get%20this%20movie%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20tight%20window%20and%20another%20project%20already%20in%20the%20works%20that%20had%20been%20greenlit%2C%20the%20director%20dropped%20out%2C%20which%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20Feig%2C%20who%20had%20been%20making%20it%20known%20around%20Hollywood%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20a%20thriller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20on%20a%20Zoom%20with%20him%2C%20and%20he%20had%20read%20all%20the%20books%3B%20he%20knew%20it%20all%20inside%20and%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20also%2C%20he%20brought%20a%20tone%20to%20this%20film%20that%20is%20slightly%20different%20than%20the%20tone%20of%20the%20book%3B%20Paul%20brought%20out%20a%20release%20valve%20of%20comedy%20that%20allows%20an%20audience%20to%20toggle%20between%20gasps%20and%20laughs.%C2%A0So%20he%20was%20the%20perfect%20director.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20October%2C%20Feig%20and%20Seyfried%20had%20signed%20on%2C%20and%20that%20was%20enough%20for%20Lionsgate%20to%20greenlight%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20brisk%2032-day%20shoot%20in%20New%20Jersey%20in%20January%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282da232c-dbff-4dc5-ad37-2eabe58b53bc%5C%22%3EFacing%20off%20against%20%26quot%3BAvatar%26quot%3B%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20secret%20sauce%20to%20box%20office%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Housemaid%20cast%20and%20producers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696f73bda645d11881879bf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223643%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELaura%20Fischer%2C%20Todd%20Lieberman%2C%20Paul%20Feig%2C%20Amanda%20Seyfried%2C%20Sydney%20Sweeney%2C%20Brandon%20Sklenar%2C%20and%20Carly%20Elter%20at%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAxelle%2FBauer-Griffin%2FFilmMagic%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lionsgate%20called%20Lieberman%20shortly%20after%20production%20wrapped%20to%20tell%20him%20it%20was%20slating%20the%20movie%20for%20a%20Christmas%20Day%20release%2C%20he%20didn't%20feel%20panicked.%20Yes%2C%20the%20movie%20would%20have%20to%20go%20up%20against%20the%20latest%20installment%20of%20the%20famously%20lucrative%20%26quot%3BAvatar%26quot%3B%20franchise%20at%20the%20box%20office%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BAvatar%3A%20Fire%20and%20Ash%26quot%3B%20was%20slated%20for%20December%2019%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20saw%20that%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20shine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20had%20strong%20test%20screenings.%20But%20there%20was%20one%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20family%20movie%2C%20so%20how%20are%20we%20going%20to%20compete%20where%20families%20are%20going%20to%20the%20theater%3F%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20wondered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20Lionsgate%20chairman%20Adam%20Fogelson%20and%20head%20of%20domestic%20distribution%20Kevin%20Grayson%20made%20an%20adjustment%2C%20moving%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20release%20date%20from%20Christmas%20Day%20to%20December%2019.%20Though%20it%20would%20now%20have%20the%20same%20opening%20day%20as%20%26quot%3BAvatar%3A%20Fire%20%26amp%3B%20Ash%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20gave%20the%20movie%20some%20runway%20to%20gain%20traction%20before%20the%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20first%20week%20served%20as%20additional%20word%20of%20mouth%20and%20was%20basically%20marketing%20screenings%20for%20the%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20Lieberman%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20once%20Christmas%20was%20over%20and%20people%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20theaters%20with%20their%20families%2C%20our%20numbers%20really%20kicked%20into%20gear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20January%20hit%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20was%20overperforming%20its%20industry%20projections%2C%20with%20box%20office%20only%20dropping%20around%2020%25%20over%20consecutive%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20fans%20didn't%20know%20was%20that%20Lieberman%20already%20had%20the%20pieces%20in%20place%20for%20a%20sequel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20who%20works%20for%20me%20knows%20I%20don't%20talk%20about%20sequels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20going%20to%20give%20credit%20to%20Paul%20%5BFeig%5D%20and%20his%20producing%20partner%2C%20Laura%20Fischer.%20While%20we%20were%20in%20post%2C%20they%20said%2C%20'Shouldn't%20we%20be%20thinking%20about%20getting%20prepared%20for%20the%20second%20one%3F'%20I%20went%20against%20my%20own%20superstitions%2C%20and%20I%20agreed%20we%20should%20be%20prepared.%20So%20we%20brought%20Rebecca%20back%20in%2C%20and%20she%20turned%20in%20a%20draft%20that%20was%20excellent%2C%20and%20the%20moment%20the%20movie%20hit%20a%20certain%20benchmark%20for%20Lionsgate%2C%20we%20had%20the%20sequel.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid's%20Secret%26quot%3B%20goes%20into%20production%20sometime%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20pulling%20off%20unlikely%20success%20stories%2C%20Lieberman%20said%20the%20most%20satisfying%20part%20of%20his%20job%20is%20proving%20that%20non-blockbuster%20stories%20can%20still%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20moments%20that%20give%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20moviegoing%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20people%20will%20show%20up%20in%20droves%20if%20there's%20something%20that%20feels%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-housemaid-movie-book-box-office-success-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769114378000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696f70f4a645d11881879be2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-housemaid-movie-book-box-office-success-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Made%20for%20only%20%2435%20million%2C%20the%20producer%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Housemaid%26quot%3B%20walks%20us%20through%20how%20it%20became%20a%20%24240%20million%20surprise%20hit%20at%20the%20box%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jguerrasio%40businessinsider.com%20(Jason%20Guerrasio)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-housemaid-movie-book-box-office-success-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SIR%20order%20makes%20no%20mention%20of%20citizenship%20verification%3A%20SC%20to%20EC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769114337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-127196091%2Cimgsize-991507.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsir-order-makes-no-mention-of-citizenship-verification-sc-to-ec%2Farticleshow%2F127195878.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Not%20mentioned%20expressly%2C%20admits%20EC%2C%20but%20says%20process%20transparent%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Row%20over%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20hand%20bruise%20in%20Davos%20and%20%E2%80%98missing%20medical%20records%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98Two%20years%20of%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20health%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769114127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-127195328%2Cimgsize-1079417.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime