Paramount%20Plus%20Essential%20and%20Peacock%20Premium%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20perks.%20They%20can%20select%20which%20service%20they'd%20like%20access%20to%20every%2090%20days%2C%20so%20there's%20always%20a%20chance%20to%20switch%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20the%20two%20apps.%20Walmart%20Plus%20subscriptions%20cost%20%2412.95%20a%20month%20or%20%2498%20a%20year%20and%20come%20with%20a%2030-day%20free%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229302a85d-7361-4f9c-b62f-843faa0d4bdf%5C%22%3EDoes%20Paramount%20Plus%20have%20a%20free%20trial%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Plus%20no%20longer%20offers%20a%20free%20trial.%20The%20service%20previously%20offered%20new%20customers%20a%20seven-day%20free%20trial%20before%20billing%20kicked%20in%2C%20but%20the%20streamer%20removed%20the%20trial%20offer%20in%20early%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233a7b99a-1d74-4ea2-9dd2-66ad6465887b%5C%22%3EWhat%20devices%20can%20I%20use%20to%20watch%20Paramount%20Plus%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Plus%20is%20available%20to%20stream%20across%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20devices%2C%20including%20mobile%20devices%2C%20smart%20TVs%2C%20computers%2C%20streaming%20players%2C%20set-top%20boxes%2C%20and%20gaming%20consoles.%20Some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20options%20include%20the%20Android%20app%20(phones%20and%20tablets)%2C%20iOS%20app%20(iPhones%20and%20iPads)%2C%20Apple%20TV%2C%20Chromecast%2C%20Fire%20TV%2C%20LG%20TV%2C%20PlayStation%205%2C%20Xbox%2C%20Roku%2C%20and%20Samsung%20TV%2C%20among%20others.%20You%20can%20find%20a%20full%20list%20of%20supported%20devices%20on%20the%20Paramount%20Plus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.paramountplus.com%2Fs%2Farticle%2FPI-On-which-devices-can-I-watch-Paramount%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Compatible%20devices%20vary%20by%20country%2C%20and%20users%20must%20be%20running%20updated%20versions%20of%20relevant%20software.%20For%20example%2C%20iPhones%20and%20iPads%20must%20be%20running%20iOS%2016%20or%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a297e0ee-0b6e-4b87-a6e2-193a2ba16223%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20download%20on%20Paramount%20Plus%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Paramount%20Plus%20Premium%20tier%20allows%20subscribers%20to%20download%20films%20and%20TV%20shows%20to%20watch%20offline.%20Most%20shows%20and%20select%20movies%20are%20available%20to%20download.%20This%20option%20is%20not%20available%20for%20the%20Essential%20plan.%20You%20can%20only%20download%20on%20iPhones%2FiPads%20running%20iOS%2016%2B%20and%20Android%20tablets%2Fphones%20running%20Android%206%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227339%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Paramount%20Plus%20logo%20is%20displayed%20on%20a%20mobile%20phone%20with%20the%20company's%20branding%20seen%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69723f88d3c7faef0eccba51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Raa%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9e1595f-f69a-4850-8028-63ef8a385133%5C%22%3EWhat%20shows%20and%20movies%20are%20on%20Paramount%20Plus%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Plus%20hosts%20a%20variety%20of%20content%20from%20CBS%2C%20Paramount%20Pictures%2C%20MTV%2C%20Comedy%20Central%2C%20and%20other%20Paramount%20properties.%20It's%20the%20best%20streaming%20service%20if%20you're%20looking%20to%20watch%20new%20episodes%20of%20beloved%20CBS%20series%20the%20day%20after%20they%20air%20on%20the%20network%2C%20or%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20past%20seasons.%20%26quot%3BTracker%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BNCIS%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFire%20Country%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMatlock%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BGhosts%26quot%3B%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20currently-airing%20shows%20you%20can%20stream%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20streaming%20service%20is%20also%20the%20home%20to%20several%20hit%20originals%2C%20including%20the%20%26quot%3BCriminal%20Minds%26quot%3B%20continuation%2C%20%26quot%3BCriminal%20Minds%3A%20Evolution%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20all%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%26quot%3B%20spin-offs%2C%20including%20%26quot%3B1883%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B1923%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20forthcoming%20series%20%26quot%3BThe%20Madison%26quot%3B%20(however%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20head%20to%20Peacock%20to%20stream%20the%20original%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%26quot%3B%20series).%20Other%20popular%20originals%20include%20additional%20series%20from%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%26quot%3B%20co-creator%20Taylor%20Sheridan%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BLandman%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMayor%20of%20Kingstown%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLioness%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTulsa%20King.%26quot%3B%20New%20episodes%20of%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Park%26quot%3B%20(and%20the%20full%2028-season%20back%20catalog)%20are%20also%20available%20on%20Paramount%20Plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubscribers%20can%20also%20catch%20seasons%20of%20other%20popular%20shows%20from%20Paramount-owned%20networks%2C%20like%20Comedy%20Central's%20%26quot%3BBroad%20City%26quot%3B%20and%20Nickelodeon's%20%26quot%3BSpongeBob%20SquarePants.%26quot%3B%20New%20seasons%20of%20%26quot%3BRuPaul's%20Drag%20Race%26quot%3B%20end%20up%20on%20Paramount%20Plus%2C%20but%20not%20until%20after%20the%20full%20season%20has%20finished%20airing%20on%20MTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20movies%2C%20the%20streaming%20service%20typically%20gets%20the%20latest%20releases%20from%20Paramount%20Pictures%20once%20they're%20out%20of%20theaters%20and%20available%20for%20streaming.%20Recent%20additions%20include%20%26quot%3BThe%20Running%20Man%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BRoofman.%26quot%3B%20The%20streamer%20also%20has%20a%20massive%20selection%20of%20older%20movies%2C%20including%20both%20Paramount%20Pictures%20originals%20(such%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BMission%3A%20Impossible%26quot%3B%20franchise)%20and%20films%20from%20other%20companies%20(like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Martian%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BZero%20Dark%20Thirty%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubscribers%20who%20opt%20for%20the%20Premium%20tier%20will%20also%20unlock%20Showtime%20series%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BDexter%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BRay%20Donovan%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBillions%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BCalifornication%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20L%20Word%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Affair.%26quot%3B%20We've%20noticed%20that%20newer%20Showtime%20series%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BYellowjackets%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDexter%3A%20Resurrection%2C%26quot%3B%20typically%20drop%20new%20episodes%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20early%20on%20Paramount%20Plus%20ahead%20of%20their%20weekly%20broadcast%20premieres.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213bc73de-b9d6-4506-b3af-486aa7264778%5C%22%3EWhat%20sports%20are%20on%20Paramount%20Plus%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESports%20are%20also%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20alluring%20component%20of%20Paramount%20Plus's%20offerings.%20If%20you%20have%20the%20Premium%20tier%2C%20you%20can%20live%20stream%20any%20sporting%20event%20airing%20on%20CBS%2C%20which%20is%20particularly%20handy%20for%20March%20Madness%20and%20The%20Masters%20tournaments.%20All%20tiers%20of%20Paramount%20Plus%20include%20access%20to%20NFL%20on%20CBS%20games%2C%20Champions%20League%20matches%2C%20and%20UFC%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Plus%20now%20holds%20the%20broadcast%20rights%20to%20UFC%2C%20taking%20over%20from%20ESPN%20in%202026%20as%20part%20of%20a%20seven-year%20deal.%20Unlike%20ESPN%2C%20major%20numbered%20events%20won't%20require%20an%20additional%20pay-per-view%20(PPV)%20fee.%20Instead%2C%20all%20subscribers%20(whether%20you%20have%20an%20Essential%20or%20Premium%20plan)%20will%20be%20able%20to%20stream%20all%20UFC%20coverage.%20Select%20UFC%20events%20will%20also%20air%20on%20CBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20information%2C%20check%20out%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https