Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20forward%20deploy%20and%20build%20your%20robots%20as%20close%20to%20the%20environment%20as%20possible.%20And%20that%20gives%20you%20the%20information%20and%20dataset%20that%20doesn't%20exist%20anywhere%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20anywhere%20on%20YouTube%2C%20about%20what%20these%20environments%20are%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20Loosararian%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniela%20Rus%2C%20the%20director%20of%20MIT's%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Laboratory%2C%20said%20there%20was%20a%20gap%20between%20robots'%20ability%20to%20perform%20tasks%20in%20a%20laboratory%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20take%20on%20jobs%20traditionally%20done%20by%20humans%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Davos%20panel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69723414d3c7faef0eccb8fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIndustry%20leaders%20discussed%20robotics%20at%20a%20Davos%20panel%20hosted%20by%20Business%20Insider's%20Jamie%20Heller.%3Cp%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20give%20you%20a%20robot%20that%20will%20fold%20your%20laundry%20and%20load%20your%20dishwasher%2C%20but%20it%20might%20cost%20you%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERus%20said%20bridging%20that%20gap%20would%20require%20advancements%20in%20a%20humanoid%20robot's%20ability%20to%20perceive%20and%20manipulate%20the%20world%20through%20improved%20sensors%20and%20new%20AI%20models%20that%20can%20handle%20situations%20the%20robot%20may%20not%20have%20encountered%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShao%20Tianlan%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Chinese%20AI%20and%20robotics%20firm%20Mech-Mind%2C%20said%20that%20one%20big%20barrier%20to%20making%20humanoid%20robots%20useful%20in%20a%20factory%20environment%20was%20developing%20the%20capacity%20for%20them%20to%20learn%20directly%20from%20their%20human%20coworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20to%20deploy%20a%20robot%2C%20I%20would%20say%20demonstration%20is%20the%20most%20intuitive%20way%20to%20tell%20robots%20what%20to%20do.%20That's%20exactly%20how%20we%20humans%20teach%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETianlan%2C%20who%20said%20that%20Mech-Mind%20had%20delivered%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20%26quot%3Bintelligent%20robots%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%2C%20added%20that%20he%20did%20not%20believe%20humanoid%20robots%20needed%20%26quot%3BEinstein-level%26quot%3B%20intelligence%20to%20perform%20useful%20tasks%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20predicted%20that%20robots%20would%20take%20on%20some%20jobs%20performed%20by%20humans%20in%20controlled%20environments%2C%20such%20as%20in%20logistics%20and%20some%20service%20industries%2C%20in%20the%20next%20%26quot%3Bfew%20hundred%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumanoid%20robots%20are%20riding%20a%20wave%20of%20hype%20as%20companies%20like%20Tesla%20and%20Figure%20prepare%20to%20begin%20large-scale%20manufacturing%20of%20their%20machines.%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20made%20bold%20predictions%20about%20the%20company's%20Optimus%20robot%2C%20saying%20it%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-optimus-eliminate-poverty-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeliminate%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-elon-musk-said-about-robotics-robotaxi-optimus-media-blitz-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20product%20of%20all%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20most%20humanoid%20robots%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20deployed%20in%20real-world%20environments.%20Many%20humanoid%20robot%20demos%20are%20staged%20in%20tightly%20controlled%20settings%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-optimus-humanoid-robot-training-elon-musk-2025-11%5C%22%20t